{"115138":{"value":{"Media":{"id":115138,"idMal":41261,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/115138","status":"FINISHED","season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2020,"type":"ANIME","format":"OVA","bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/115138-KDpOVgLKv36A.jpg","episodes":2,"synonyms":["Gishi wa Yanmama Junyuu-chuu","My Big Sister Is Breastfeeding","My Former-Delinquent Sister is Breastfeeding","형수는 양마마 수유중"],"isAdult":true,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","meanScore":74,"description":"Based on the CG collections by Chinjao Girl. (チンジャオ娘。).\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\"What's wrong? Do you wanna suck my tits? lol\"\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nPlaced before scenes of his big sister's defenseless breastfeeding, this little brother finally gives way to his sexual drive...!\u003cbr\u003e\nWill he be able to impregnate her before her husband does!?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: DLsite English)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: It has live-action AV adaptations: EYAN-181 (2022/05/17) and SONE-201 (2024/05/28).\u003c/i\u003e","genres":["Hentai"],"duration":17,"title":{"native":"義姉はヤンママ授乳中","romaji":"Ane wa Yanmama Junyuu-chuu","userPreferred":"Ane wa Yanmama Junyuu-chuu"},"coverImage":{"color":"#e4935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx115138-oZHgSvWaOeSp.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx115138-oZHgSvWaOeSp.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx115138-oZHgSvWaOeSp.jpg"},"startDate":{"day":5,"month":6,"year":2020},"endDate":{"day":3,"month":7,"year":2020},"relations":{}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T06:25:55.211439+03:00"},"166613":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/166613-drS86exJlIjG.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e49328","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx166613-uHB8q3D4qbon.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx166613-uHB8q3D4qbon.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx166613-uHB8q3D4qbon.jpg"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eJigokuraku\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":29,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Mystery","Supernatural"],"id":166613,"idMal":55825,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1772376240,"episode":8,"timeUntilAiring":253920},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/100994-mEIqjSzFKysR.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d61a86","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx100994-f6CMjiQQNVeS.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx100994-f6CMjiQQNVeS.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx100994-f6CMjiQQNVeS.png"},"description":"Gabimaru the Hollow is one of the most vicious assassins ever to come out of the ninja village of Iwagakure. He’s ruthlessly efficient, but a betrayal results in him being handed a death sentence. He has only one hope—in order to earn his freedom, he must travel to a long-hidden island and recover an elixir that will make the shogun immortal. Failure is not an option. On this island, heaven and hell are just a hair’s breadth away.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: VIZ Media)","endDate":{"day":25,"month":1,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Mystery","Supernatural"],"id":100994,"idMal":112318,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/100994","startDate":{"day":23,"month":1,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Hell's Paradise","Paradition","Heavenhell","Jigoku Raku","Piekielny Raj","지옥락","สุขาวดีอเวจี"],"title":{"english":"Hell’s Paradise: Jigokuraku","native":"地獄楽","romaji":"Jigokuraku","userPreferred":"Jigokuraku"},"trailer":{"id":"C7iGt19x_F4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/C7iGt19x_F4/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/128893-pAA7PjY8l7dy.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb35","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx128893-Gc2t8b8M0mVu.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx128893-Gc2t8b8M0mVu.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx128893-Gc2t8b8M0mVu.jpg"},"description":"The Edo period is nearing its end. Gabimaru, a shinobi formerly known as the strongest in Iwagakure who is now a death row convict, is told that he will be acquitted and set free if he can bring back the Elixir of Life from an island that is rumored to be the Buddhist pure land Sukhavati. In hopes of reuniting with his beloved wife, Gabimaru heads to the island along with the executioner Yamada Asaemon Sagiri. Upon arriving there, they encounter other death row convicts in search of the Elixir of Life... as well as a host of unknown creatures, eerie manmade statues, and the hermits who rule the island. Can Gabimaru find the Elixir of Life on this mysterious island and make it back home alive?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":1,"month":7,"year":2023},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Mystery","Supernatural"],"id":128893,"idMal":46569,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2023,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/128893","startDate":{"day":1,"month":4,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Hell’s Paradise: Jigokuraku","สุขาวดีอเวจี","Адский рай"],"title":{"english":"Hell’s Paradise","native":"地獄楽","romaji":"Jigokuraku","userPreferred":"Jigokuraku"},"trailer":{"id":"8BIaDDN-r3o","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/8BIaDDN-r3o/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"PREQUEL"}]},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/166613","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Hell’s Paradise: Jigokuraku Season 2","สุขาวดีอเวจี","Адский рай"],"title":{"english":"Hell’s Paradise Season 2","native":"地獄楽 第二期","romaji":"Jigokuraku 2nd Season","userPreferred":"Jigokuraku 2nd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"JLe_NUnAZVs","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JLe_NUnAZVs/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T19:12:00.043958+03:00"},"166617":{"value":{"Media":{"id":166617,"idMal":55830,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/166617","status":"RELEASING","season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"type":"ANIME","format":"TV","bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/166617-P4w3p0H4lE1O.jpg","episodes":13,"synonyms":["Судьба/Странная подделка"],"isAdult":false,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","meanScore":83,"description":"In a Holy Grail War, Mages (Masters) and their Heroic Spirits (Servants) fight for the control of the Holy Grail—an omnipotent wish-granting device said to fulfill any desire. Years have passed since the end of the Fifth Holy Grail War in Japan. Now, signs portend the emergence of a new Holy Grail in the western American city of Snowfield. Sure enough, Masters and Servants begin to gather... \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nA missing Servant class...\u003cbr\u003e\nImpossible Servant summonings...\u003cbr\u003e\nA nation shrouded in secrecy...\u003cbr\u003e\nAnd a city created as a battleground.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nIn the face of such irregularities, the Holy Grail War is twisted and driven into the depth of madness. Let the curtain rise on a masquerade of humans and heroes, made to dance upon the stage of a false Holy Grail. \u003ci\u003eThis is a Holy Grail War covered in lies.\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official Site, Aniplex USA, edited)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n•  \u003ci\u003eSpecial premiere of Episode 1 in its English Dub occurred in Los Angeles at the Fate 20th Anniversary Showcase event and as well through Crunchyroll’s YouTube Channel on November 23, 2024 before the Japanese television premiere.\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n•  \u003ci\u003eThe Japanese advanced premiere occurred during the \"Fate New Year's Eve TV Special 2024\" on December 31, 2024.\u003c/i\u003e","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Mystery","Supernatural"],"duration":25,"trailer":{"id":"k1G8EvZg_BY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/k1G8EvZg_BY/hqdefault.jpg"},"title":{"english":"Fate/strange Fake","native":"Fate/strange Fake","romaji":"Fate/strange Fake","userPreferred":"Fate/strange Fake"},"coverImage":{"color":"#1a1af1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png"},"startDate":{"day":3,"month":1,"year":2026},"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774103400,"episode":12,"timeUntilAiring":559836},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":86753,"idMal":83923,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/86753","status":"RELEASING","type":"MANGA","format":"MANGA","bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/86753-J0xAuASfT348.jpg","synonyms":["フェイト/ストレンジフェイク","페이트 스트레인지 페이크"],"isAdult":false,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","meanScore":81,"description":"The plot centers around a Grail War faultily copied from the Third Holy Grail War in Fuyuki. After the end of the third Grail War, an organization from the United States that has magi separate from the London based Mage Association as members took data from Fuyuki's Grail War and planned their own ritual. After seventy years, they used the city Snowfield as the Sacred Land for their own Grail War. They were unable to successfully copy every aspect of the ritual, which lead to it acting only as an imitation that has lost the Saber class and allowed for the summoning of strange Servants due to the definition of a \"hero\" being blurred.","genres":["Action","Drama","Fantasy","Supernatural"],"title":{"native":"Fate/strange Fake","romaji":"Fate/strange Fake","userPreferred":"Fate/strange Fake"},"coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae35","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx86753-U39qnzjrfCLH.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx86753-U39qnzjrfCLH.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx86753-U39qnzjrfCLH.jpg"},"startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2015},"endDate":{}},"relationType":"ALTERNATIVE"},{"node":{"id":50006,"idMal":83903,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/50006","status":"RELEASING","type":"MANGA","format":"NOVEL","bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/50006-9feJaDhW14aS.jpg","synonyms":["フェイト/ストレンジフェイク","Fake/states night","페이트 스트레인지 페이크"],"isAdult":false,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","meanScore":86,"description":"The stage: the city of Snowfield in the western U.S., far from Fuyuki. There, a \"false Holy Grail War\", quite unlike the original Holy Grail War, unfolds. There were those who had been keeping an eye on the auguries of the Holy Grail in Snowfield. According to an investigation by the Mage's Association, the Holy Grail War system in Snowfield was an imitation of the one in Fuyuki. What's more, the system was incomplete, leading to the exclusion of one of the seven classes and the selection of beings as Servants who ordinarily could not be summoned. It was, verily, a strange fake. As an organ of the U.S. government executes its various plots, the Servants are summoned one after another...","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Mystery","Supernatural"],"title":{"native":"Fate/strange Fake","romaji":"Fate/strange Fake","userPreferred":"Fate/strange Fake"},"coverImage":{"color":"#e44350","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx50006-SzwC3M73aM2X.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx50006-SzwC3M73aM2X.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx50006-SzwC3M73aM2X.jpg"},"startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2015},"endDate":{}},"relationType":"SOURCE"},{"node":{"id":154966,"idMal":53127,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/154966","status":"FINISHED","season":"SUMMER","type":"ANIME","format":"SPECIAL","seasonYear":2023,"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/154966-xIvcAtzwOZk6.jpg","episodes":1,"synonyms":["Судьба/Странная подделка. Шёпот рассвета"],"isAdult":false,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","meanScore":81,"description":"Years after the Fifth Holy Grail War in Japan, strange reports surface of one appearing in America. Attracting new Mages and Servants, the question is raised about the relic’s authenticity. As the city of Snowfield is turned into a bloody battleground, specific details seem wrong. Is it possible someone is manipulating this twisted little play, and if so, does this mean the true Holy Grail exists?\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Special premiere occurred in Los Angeles at Anime Expo before the Japanese television premiere on July 2, 2023.\u003c/i\u003e","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Mystery","Supernatural"],"duration":55,"trailer":{"id":"dQOtt9tW0F4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/dQOtt9tW0F4/hqdefault.jpg"},"title":{"english":"Fate/strange Fake -Whispers of Dawn-","native":"Fate/strange Fake -Whispers of Dawn-","romaji":"Fate/strange Fake: Whispers of Dawn","userPreferred":"Fate/strange Fake: Whispers of Dawn"},"coverImage":{"color":"#50c9f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx154966-eQRCmSrCh96j.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx154966-eQRCmSrCh96j.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx154966-eQRCmSrCh96j.png"},"startDate":{"day":2,"month":7,"year":2023},"endDate":{"day":2,"month":7,"year":2023}},"relationType":"PREQUEL"}]}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T05:59:24.657432+03:00"},"167152":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/167152-6QxZG8Dmf1EL.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx167152-u0cBZkqDowHP.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx167152-u0cBZkqDowHP.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx167152-u0cBZkqDowHP.jpg"},"description":"In a world where heroism is a punishment, Xylo Forbartz, a condemned goddess killer, battles endless hordes of monstrous abominations as part of Penal Hero Unit 9004. Death is no escape, only a cycle of resurrection and relentless combat. But when Xylo encounters a mysterious new goddess, their unlikely alliance sparks a rebellion that could shatter the chains of eternal punishment.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- The first episode aired with a runtime of ~58 minutes as opposed to the standard 24 minute long episode.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Initially scheduled to air in October, 2025 \u003c/i\u003e","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":26,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":167152,"idMal":56009,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773322200,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":559227},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f16b35","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx142687-BFy2lofGgPKx.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx142687-BFy2lofGgPKx.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx142687-BFy2lofGgPKx.jpg"},"description":"Heroism—a punishment for only the worst criminals. Those sentenced to the fate of a hero are forced to fight at the front lines against the demon king’s army—and if they die, all they can expect is to be revived and continue the battle. But when their leader, convicted of killing a goddess, meets another goddess himself, the contract they forge may be enough to change the world…\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Yen Press)","endDate":{},"format":"NOVEL","genres":["Action","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":142687,"idMal":156106,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/142687","startDate":{"day":17,"month":9,"year":2021},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Sentenced to Brave Punishment"],"title":{"english":"Sentenced to Be a Hero","native":"勇者刑に処す　懲罰勇者9004隊刑務記録","romaji":"Yuusha Kei ni Shosu: Choubatsu Yuusha 9004-tai Keimu Kiroku","userPreferred":"Yuusha Kei ni Shosu: Choubatsu Yuusha 9004-tai Keimu Kiroku"},"trailer":{"id":"nKYGfmykWCE","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/nKYGfmykWCE/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"},{"node":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#863528","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx164543-rACx6Osg3H26.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx164543-rACx6Osg3H26.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx164543-rACx6Osg3H26.jpg"},"description":"Sinned heroes will save this world...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nBeing sentenced to Heroship was the most severe punishment one could be given. Heroes would be sent to the frontline of a never-ending battle against the demon lords. Not even death could relieve them on their duty.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nThere was no end to prison sentence. Even if they fought for a hundred years, they would still not be released. Only by killing every last demon lord would they be pardoned for their crimes. And...that was no more than a pipe dream. However, things might be different for XYRO, Penal Hero Unit 9004. He accidentally meets a goddess...and she asks him to be her knight!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: KADOKAWA Global)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":164543,"idMal":151361,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":69,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/164543","startDate":{"day":25,"month":3,"year":2022},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Sentenced to Brave Punishment","Punishment for Brave Hero: 9004 Corps Prison Record","Sentenced to Hero Punishment: The Service Records of the 9004th Penitent Hero Corps"],"title":{"english":"Sentenced to Be a Hero: The Prison Records of Penal Hero Unit 9004","native":"勇者刑に処す 懲罰勇者9004隊刑務記録","romaji":"Yuusha Kei ni Shosu: Choubatsu Yuusha 9004-tai Keimu Kiroku","userPreferred":"Yuusha Kei ni Shosu: Choubatsu Yuusha 9004-tai Keimu Kiroku"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"ALTERNATIVE"}]},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/167152","startDate":{"day":3,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["ผู้กล้าโทษประหาร : บันทึกการรับโทษของหน่วยผู้กล้าต้องโทษ 9004","용사형에 처함"],"title":{"english":"Sentenced to Be a Hero","native":"勇者刑に処す　懲罰勇者9004隊刑務記録","romaji":"Yuusha Kei ni Shosu: Choubatsu Yuusha 9004-tai Keimu Kiroku","userPreferred":"Yuusha Kei ni Shosu: Choubatsu Yuusha 9004-tai Keimu Kiroku"},"trailer":{"id":"GcRs1JC7xeg","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/GcRs1JC7xeg/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-06T05:09:33.079258+03:00"},"172463":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/172463-3J2o3qQZadFJ.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5093d6","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx172463-LnXqHzt74SJL.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx172463-LnXqHzt74SJL.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx172463-LnXqHzt74SJL.jpg"},"description":"The third season of \u003ci\u003eJujutsu Kaisen\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAfter the Shibuya Incident, a deadly jujutsu battle known as the Culling Game orchestrated by Noritoshi Kamo erupts across ten colonies in Japan.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nHaunted by guilt over the mass killings in Shibuya and wary of Sukuna’s interest in Fushiguro, Itadori chooses not to return to Jujutsu High. Instead, he teams up with Choso to exorcise the countless cursed spirits unleashed by Noritoshi Kamo.\nAmid this chaos, the Jujutsu Headquarters revokes Yuji Itadori’s suspended death sentence and appoints special-grade sorcerer Yuta Okkotsu as his executioner. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nNewly awakened modern sorcerers and resurrected ancient ones,  now fighting as players in the Culling Game, collide with conflicting motives, driving the world once more toward an age ruled by jujutsu.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: TOHO Animation)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":27,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Drama","Supernatural"],"id":172463,"idMal":57658,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773329160,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":495772},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/101517-FrJtb3Th3HtF.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a15d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx101517-H3TdM3g5ZUe9.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx101517-H3TdM3g5ZUe9.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx101517-H3TdM3g5ZUe9.jpg"},"description":"Although Yuji Itadori looks like your average teenager, his immense physical strength is something to behold! Every sports club wants him to join, but Itadori would rather hang out with the school outcasts in the Occult Research Club. One day, the club manages to get their hands on a sealed cursed object. Little do they know the terror they’ll unleash when they break the seal…\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: VIZ Media)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Ranked 1st in Japan's Bookstore Employees Top Manga of 2018.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Nominated for the 25th Annual Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize in 2021.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Nominated for the 65th Shogakukan Manga Award in the Shounen Category in 2019.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":30,"month":9,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Drama","Supernatural"],"id":101517,"idMal":113138,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/101517","startDate":{"day":5,"month":3,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Sorcery Fight","주술회전","咒术回战","Guerra de Hechiceros","Batalha de Feiticeiros","JJK","มหาเวทย์ผนึกมาร","Chú thuật hồi chiến","Магическая битва","La guerra màgica","Prokleté války","咒術迴戰","Contiendas de Brujería","Lanet Savaşları"],"title":{"english":"Jujutsu Kaisen","native":"呪術廻戦","romaji":"Jujutsu Kaisen","userPreferred":"Jujutsu Kaisen"},"trailer":{"id":"R60IExw7v8A","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/R60IExw7v8A/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/145064-esDtAY2He7sk.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#a178d6","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx145064-hSNRJM03pvv1.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx145064-hSNRJM03pvv1.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx145064-hSNRJM03pvv1.jpg"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eJujutsu Kaisen\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nThe past comes to light when second-year students Satoru Gojou and Suguru Getou are tasked with escorting young Riko Amanai to Master Tengen. But when a non-sorcerer user tries to kill them, their mission to protect the Star Plasma Vessel threatens to turn them into bitter enemies and cement their destinies—one as the world’s strongest sorcerer, and the other its most twisted curse user!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":12,"year":2023},"episodes":23,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Drama","Supernatural"],"id":145064,"idMal":51009,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":86,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2023,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/145064","startDate":{"day":6,"month":7,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["呪術廻戦 懐玉・玉折／渋谷事変 ","Jujutsu Kaisen: Kaigyoku Gyokusetsu / Shibuya Jihen","Jujutsu Kaisen: Hidden Inventory / Premature Death","JJK2","咒術迴戰  第二季","มหาเวทย์ผนึกมาร ภาค 2 ","咒术回战 2","2جوجوتسو كايسن ","Jujutsu Kaisen: Shibuya Incident"],"title":{"english":"JUJUTSU KAISEN Season 2","native":"呪術廻戦 第2期","romaji":"Jujutsu Kaisen 2nd Season","userPreferred":"Jujutsu Kaisen 2nd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"O6qVieflwqs","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/O6qVieflwqs/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"PREQUEL"},{"node":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e49335","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx204066-Gb5k7j6Cpbng.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx204066-Gb5k7j6Cpbng.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx204066-Gb5k7j6Cpbng.jpg"},"description":"Movie compilation of the Shibuya Incident Arc from the second season of \u003ci\u003eJujutsu Kaisen\u003c/i\u003e and the first two episodes of the third season's Culling Game Arc.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nA veil abruptly descends over the busy Shibuya area amid the bustling Halloween crowds, trapping countless civilians inside. Satoru Gojo, the strongest jujutsu sorcerer, steps into the chaos. But lying in wait are curse users and spirits scheming to seal him away.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nYuji Itadori, accompanied by his classmates and other top-tier jujutsu sorcerers, enters the fray in an unprecedented clash of curses — the Shibuya Incident.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nIn the aftermath, ten colonies across Japan are transformed into dens of curses in a plan orchestrated by Noritoshi Kamo, the most wicked sorcerer in history. As the deadly Culling Game starts, Special Grade sorcerer Yuta Okkotsu is assigned to carry out Yuji’s execution for his perceived crimes.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: GKIDS)","duration":88,"endDate":{"day":7,"month":11,"year":2025},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Drama","Supernatural"],"id":204066,"idMal":62392,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2025,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/204066","startDate":{"day":7,"month":11,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["JJK Movie","JUJUTSU KAISEN: Execution"],"title":{"english":"JUJUTSU KAISEN: Execution -Shibuya Incident x The Culling Game Begins-","native":"呪術廻戦『渋谷事変 特別編集版』×『死滅回游 先行上映』","romaji":"Jujutsu Kaisen: Shibuya Jihen Tokubetsu Henshuu-ban x Shimetsu Kaiyuu Senkou Jouei","userPreferred":"Jujutsu Kaisen: Shibuya Jihen Tokubetsu Henshuu-ban x Shimetsu Kaiyuu Senkou Jouei"},"trailer":{"id":"VEjVqXiiUNY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VEjVqXiiUNY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"PREQUEL"}]},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/172463","startDate":{"day":9,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Jujutsu Kaisen 3rd Season","呪術廻戦 第3期","JJK3","มหาเวทย์ผนึกมาร จรดลล้างบาง พาร์ต 1"],"title":{"english":"JUJUTSU KAISEN Season 3: The Culling Game Part 1","native":"呪術廻戦 死滅回游 前編","romaji":"Jujutsu Kaisen: Shimetsu Kaiyuu - Zenpen","userPreferred":"Jujutsu Kaisen: Shimetsu Kaiyuu - Zenpen"},"trailer":{"id":"ruX3rIj3--w","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ruX3rIj3--w/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-07T00:43:08.750813+03:00"},"182255":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/182255-wyHvp6zJbWsO.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5dc9f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx182255-butzrqd4I0aC.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx182255-butzrqd4I0aC.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx182255-butzrqd4I0aC.jpg"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eSousou no Frieren\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":27,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":10,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":182255,"idMal":59978,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":89,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773410400,"episode":8,"timeUntilAiring":577510},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/118586-R1c7mc72oPvS.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx118586-CXKgWikBFQgS.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx118586-CXKgWikBFQgS.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx118586-CXKgWikBFQgS.jpg"},"description":"The adventure is over but life goes on for an elf mage just beginning to learn what living is all about.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nElf mage Frieren and her courageous fellow adventurers have defeated the Demon King and brought peace to the land. With the great struggle over, they all go their separate ways to live a quiet life. But as an elf, Frieren, nearly immortal, will long outlive the rest of her former party. How will she come to terms with the mortality of her friends? How can she find fulfillment in her own life, and can she learn to understand what life means to the humans around her? Frieren begins a new journey to find the answer.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: VIZ Media)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Winner of the Grand Prize at the 14th Manga Taisho Awards.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Nominated for the 25th Annual Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Placed 3rd at the 7th Annual Next Manga Award.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Adventure","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":118586,"idMal":126287,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":87,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/118586","startDate":{"day":28,"month":4,"year":2020},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["Frieren at the Funeral","장송의 프리렌","Frieren: Oltre la Fine del Viaggio","คำอธิษฐานในวันที่จากลา Frieren","Frieren e a Jornada para o Além","Frieren – Nach dem Ende der Reise","葬送的芙莉蓮","Frieren After \"The End\"","Frieren: Remnants of the Departed","Frieren. U kresu drogi","Frieren","FRIEREN: Más allá del fin del viaje","Проводжальниця Фрірен","Frieren: Ved reisens ende"],"title":{"english":"Frieren: Beyond Journey’s End","native":"葬送のフリーレン","romaji":"Sousou no Frieren","userPreferred":"Sousou no Frieren"},"trailer":{"id":"sIFkD5l8ZCU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/sIFkD5l8ZCU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/154587-ivXNJ23SM1xB.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#bbf1a1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx154587-qQTzQnEJJ3oB.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx154587-qQTzQnEJJ3oB.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx154587-qQTzQnEJJ3oB.jpg"},"description":"The adventure is over but life goes on for an elf mage just beginning to learn what living is all about. Elf mage Frieren and her courageous fellow adventurers have defeated the Demon King and brought peace to the land. But Frieren will long outlive the rest of her former party. How will she come to understand what life means to the people around her? Decades after their victory, the funeral of one her friends confronts Frieren with her own near immortality. Frieren sets out to fulfill the last wishes of her comrades and finds herself beginning a new adventure…\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":22,"month":3,"year":2024},"episodes":28,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":154587,"idMal":52991,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":91,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2023,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/154587","startDate":{"day":29,"month":9,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Frieren at the Funeral","장송의 프리렌","Frieren - Oltre la Fine del Viaggio","คำอธิษฐานในวันที่จากลา Frieren","Frieren e a Jornada para o Além","Frieren – Nach dem Ende der Reise","葬送的芙莉蓮","Frieren: Más allá del final del viaje","Frieren en el funeral","Sōsō no Furīren","Frieren. U kresu drogi","Frieren - Pháp sư tiễn táng","Фрирен, провожающая в последний путь","فريرن: ما وراء نهاية الرحلة","Frieren: Tras finalizar el viaje"],"title":{"english":"Frieren: Beyond Journey’s End","native":"葬送のフリーレン","romaji":"Sousou no Frieren","userPreferred":"Sousou no Frieren"},"trailer":{"id":"qgQunxD0qCk","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/qgQunxD0qCk/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"PREQUEL"},{"node":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d6d678","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b206425-WOwXsfDbHZwb.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b206425-WOwXsfDbHZwb.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b206425-WOwXsfDbHZwb.jpg"},"description":"A third batch of the \u003ci\u003e●● no Mahou\u003c/i\u003e shorts released alongside the airing of the TV anime's second season, starting with #18. Posted on the official YouTube account of TOHO animation, Frieren Twitter, and Frieren TikTok account.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003cb\u003eIncludes:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n• Mita Mono wo Kousoku Suru Mahou (見た者を拘束する魔法), released Jan 19, 2026. \u003cbr\u003e\n• Doushin ni Kaeru Mahou (童心に還る魔法), released Feb 2, 2026.\u003cbr\u003e\n• Kokoro to Karada ga Irekawaru Mahou (心と体が入れ替わる魔法), released Feb 17, 2026.\u003cbr\u003e\n• Osentaku no Mahou  (お洗濯の魔法), released Mar 2, 2026.\u003cbr\u003e","duration":1,"endDate":{},"format":"ONA","genres":["Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":206425,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":74,"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/206425","startDate":{"day":19,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Sousou no Frieren 2nd Season Mini Anime","Frieren: Beyond Journey’s End Season 2 Mini Anime","Sousou no Frieren: Marumaru no Mahou"],"title":{"native":"葬送のフリーレン ～●●の魔法～ 3クール","romaji":"Sousou no Frieren: ●● no Mahou Part 3","userPreferred":"Sousou no Frieren: ●● no Mahou Part 3"},"trailer":{"id":"WTUkzIG8ZeE","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/WTUkzIG8ZeE/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"}]},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/182255","startDate":{"day":16,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Провожающая в последний путь Фрирен 2","장송의 프리렌 2기"],"title":{"english":"Frieren: Beyond Journey’s End Season 2","native":"葬送のフリーレン 第2期","romaji":"Sousou no Frieren 2nd Season","userPreferred":"Sousou no Frieren 2nd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"RH-FcW94z00","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/RH-FcW94z00/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-07T00:34:50.226955+03:00"},"182587":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/182587-SLNmuinewbUF.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45df1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx182587-fsU8LOjmd7oj.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx182587-fsU8LOjmd7oj.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx182587-fsU8LOjmd7oj.jpg"},"description":"The third season of \u003ci\u003e[Oshi no Ko]\u003c/i\u003e.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThe story enters a new stage.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nIt's been six months since \"POP IN 2\" was released. Thanks to MEM-Cho's hard work, B-Komachi is about to get their major break. Aqua is a multi-talented entertainer, and Akane's career as a talented actress is going smoothly. Meanwhile, Kana lost the cheerfulness she once had. To track down the truth behind Ai and Goro's deaths, Ruby keeps rising in the entertainment world...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eUsing lies as a weapon.\u003c/b\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\n","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":11,"format":"TV","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":182587,"idMal":60058,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1772632800,"episode":8,"timeUntilAiring":514124},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/117195-VVYq1EEOwR0K.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e450a1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx117195-r3kf8eF0xkDJ.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx117195-r3kf8eF0xkDJ.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx117195-r3kf8eF0xkDJ.png"},"description":"Gorou is a gynecologist and idol fan who’s in shock after his favorite star, Ai, announces an impromptu hiatus. Little does Gorou realize that he’s about to forge a bond with her that defies all common sense! Lies are an idol’s weapon! \n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Yen Press)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Nominated for the 14th and 15th Manga Taisho, the 26th Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize, the 67th Shogakukan Manga Award in the general category and the 46th Kodansha Manga Award.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Winner of the 7th Next Manga Award in the print category.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Includes two extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":14,"month":11,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":117195,"idMal":126146,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/117195","startDate":{"day":23,"month":4,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Favorite Girl","My Idol's Child","[Mein*Star]","[เกิดใหม่เป็นลูกโอชิ]","Anak Idola","【OSHI NO KO】","【MOJA GWIAZDA】","【我推的孩子】","OSHI NO KO - DƯỚI ÁNH HÀO QUANG","Oshi no Ko: Minha Estrela Preferida","[Moje hvězda]","【OSHI NO KO】Mi Idol Favorita"],"title":{"english":"[Oshi no Ko]","native":"【推しの子】","romaji":"[Oshi no Ko]","userPreferred":"[Oshi no Ko]"},"trailer":{"id":"VTIB8snZ_lU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VTIB8snZ_lU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/166531-vUu7iDwUkC67.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e44343","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx166531-dAL5MsqDHUkj.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx166531-dAL5MsqDHUkj.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx166531-dAL5MsqDHUkj.jpg"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003e[Oshi no Ko]\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nAqua’s desire for revenge takes center stage as he navigates the dark underbelly of the entertainment world alongside his twin sister, Ruby. While Ruby follows in their slain mother’s footsteps to become an idol, Aqua joins a famous theater troupe in hopes of uncovering clues to the identity of his father — the man who arranged their mother’s untimely death, and the man who once starred in the same troupe Aqua hopes to infiltrate.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: HIDIVE)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":6,"month":10,"year":2024},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":166531,"idMal":55791,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2024,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/166531","startDate":{"day":3,"month":7,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["我推的孩子"],"title":{"english":"Oshi no Ko Season 2","native":"【推しの子】第2期","romaji":"[Oshi no Ko] 2nd Season","userPreferred":"[Oshi no Ko] 2nd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"QMuajQlx64c","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/QMuajQlx64c/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"PREQUEL"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/207324-MsDp7ck3PIEl.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f10d0d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx207324-BxbvjzQb7SIu.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx207324-BxbvjzQb7SIu.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx207324-BxbvjzQb7SIu.jpg"},"description":"Music video directed by Emi Fukayama for the song \u003ci\u003eSerenade\u003c/i\u003e by natori. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: The song featured in this music video also serves as the ending theme of the anime [Oshi no Ko] 3rd Season.","duration":4,"endDate":{"day":21,"month":1,"year":2026},"episodes":1,"format":"MUSIC","genres":["Drama","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":207324,"idMal":63349,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/207324","startDate":{"day":21,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Serenade (2026)","native":"セレナーデ (2026)","romaji":"Serenade (2026)","userPreferred":"Serenade (2026)"},"trailer":{"id":"gNg2Qw5R-Q4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/gNg2Qw5R-Q4/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"OTHER"}]},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/182587","startDate":{"day":14,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["[OSHI NO KO] Season 3"],"title":{"english":"【OSHI NO KO】Season 3","native":"【推しの子】第3期","romaji":"[Oshi no Ko] 3rd Season","userPreferred":"[Oshi no Ko] 3rd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"JGYY6Pui5Kc","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JGYY6Pui5Kc/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T18:11:16.778593+03:00"},"187942":{"value":{"Media":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1ae5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187942-c2cZvunJGfiE.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187942-c2cZvunJGfiE.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187942-c2cZvunJGfiE.jpg"},"description":"When Arisu Yamabuki was all alone in bed at night, he was able to find solace in the voice of a radio host who went by “Apollo.” However, one day, she simply stopped broadcasting without any explanation. Years then passed, and Arisu is now a second-year high-schooler. He makes it his mission to search for Apollo, as there is something he wants to tell her. He doesn’t know what she looks like, or even what her real name is, but he manages to get some leads on her in his school’s broadcasting club. That’s where he meets four girls who all dream to get a job where they can make full use of their voices! Just who is Apollo, and how will those four’s dreams pan out?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: K Manga)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":24,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":187942,"idMal":61211,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":70,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773756000,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":595056},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/169272-2LF1bU4MnwQc.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#c9e4f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx169272-1a2RZ43tqOdw.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx169272-1a2RZ43tqOdw.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx169272-1a2RZ43tqOdw.jpg"},"description":"When Arisu Yamabuki was all alone in bed at night, he was able to find solace in the voice of a radio host who went by “Apollo.” However, one day, she simply stopped broadcasting without any explanation. Years then passed, and Arisu is now a second-year high-schooler. He makes it his mission to search for Apollo, as there is something he wants to tell her. He doesn’t know what she looks like, or even what her real name is, but he manages to get some leads on her in his school’s broadcasting club. That’s where he meets four girls who all dream to get a job where they can make full use of their voices! Just who is Apollo, and how will those four’s dreams pan out?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: K MANGA)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":169272,"idMal":162964,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":83,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/169272","startDate":{"day":20,"month":9,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Sintonía Del Corazón a Medianoche","午夜的傾心旋律","Mayochu"],"title":{"english":"Tune In to the Midnight Heart","native":"真夜中ハートチューン","romaji":"Mayonaka Heart Tune","userPreferred":"Mayonaka Heart Tune"},"trailer":{"id":"AX2juUGZ9zI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/AX2juUGZ9zI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"}]},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187942","startDate":{"day":6,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Mayochu","จูนเสียงใจไปสุดฝัน"],"title":{"english":"Tune In to the Midnight Heart","native":"真夜中ハートチューン","romaji":"Mayonaka Heart Tune","userPreferred":"Mayonaka Heart Tune"},"trailer":{"id":"poUibdNvxPQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/poUibdNvxPQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-10T19:42:24.090025+03:00"},"207084":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/207084-QJoOYEulEDz5.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b207084-5ERIoIDjU76C.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b207084-5ERIoIDjU76C.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b207084-5ERIoIDjU76C.jpg"},"description":"In the distant future, on the outskirts left behind by the rapid concentration of advanced science and technology in urban areas, lies a remote mountain village known as Kagami Village.\u003cbr/\u003e\n“Behave yourself, or a Double will come for you.”\u003cbr/\u003e\nSuch old folklore still lingers in this village.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\nAkane Higure, a middle school student living in Kagami Village, has been eagerly awaiting the return of her older sister, Sui Higure, who is finally being discharged from the hospital after a year.\u003cbr/\u003e\nHowever, not long after her sister comes home, Akane receives a single phone call.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\n“The girl at home with you… isn’t your sister.”","duration":25,"endDate":{},"episodes":3,"format":"ONA","genres":["Mystery","Psychological","Supernatural","Thriller"],"id":207084,"idMal":63396,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"relations":{},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/207084","startDate":{"day":31,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["OneGo","Playing Sister"],"title":{"english":"Playing Sister","native":"お姉ちゃんごっこ","romaji":"Onee-chan Gokko","userPreferred":"Onee-chan Gokko"},"trailer":{"id":"Asmti3OS0W0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Asmti3OS0W0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-07T00:37:10.449448+03:00"},"21":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21-wf37VakJmZqs.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e49335","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx21-ELSYx3yMPcKM.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx21-ELSYx3yMPcKM.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx21-ELSYx3yMPcKM.jpg"},"description":"Gold Roger was known as the Pirate King, the strongest and most infamous being to have sailed the Grand Line. The capture and death of Roger by the World Government brought a change throughout the world. His last words before his death revealed the location of the greatest treasure in the world, One Piece. It was this revelation that brought about the Grand Age of Pirates, men who dreamed of finding One Piece (which promises an unlimited amount of riches and fame), and quite possibly the most coveted of titles for the person who found it, the title of the Pirate King.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nEnter Monkey D. Luffy, a 17-year-old boy that defies your standard definition of a pirate. Rather than the popular persona of a wicked, hardened, toothless pirate who ransacks villages for fun, Luffy’s reason for being a pirate is one of pure wonder; the thought of an exciting adventure and meeting new and intriguing people, along with finding One Piece, are his reasons of becoming a pirate. Following in the footsteps of his childhood hero, Luffy and his crew travel across the Grand Line, experiencing crazy adventures, unveiling dark mysteries and battling strong enemies, all in order to reach One Piece.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e*This includes following special episodes:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n- Chopperman to the Rescue! Protect the TV Station by the Shore! (Episode 336)\u003cbr\u003e\n- The Strongest Tag-Team! Luffy and Toriko's Hard Struggle! (Episode 492)\u003cbr\u003e\n- Team Formation! Save Chopper (Episode 542)\u003cbr\u003e\n- History's Strongest Collaboration vs. Glutton of the Sea (Episode 590)\u003cbr\u003e\n- 20th Anniversary! Special Romance Dawn (Episode 907)","duration":24,"endDate":{},"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":21,"idMal":21,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":88,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1775398560,"episode":1156,"timeUntilAiring":2569248},"relations":{"edges":[{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/466-uS8J4XwJ35Ws.png","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e49328","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/nx466-bVP54I7dCB2F.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx466-bVP54I7dCB2F.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/nx466-bVP54I7dCB2F.jpg"},"description":"While Luffy and his crew of Zoro and Nami are starving on their small boat, they are attacked by a large monster. Nami is taken away, while Luffy and Zoro wash up on shore. There they meet a young girl, Medaka, and learn of the sad history of the island. The evil Pirate Ganzack has taken away all the men in the village and enslaved them, including Medaka's father. Now Luffy, Zoro, and Medaka must infiltrate Ganzack's base in order to rescue the villagers and Nami. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":28,"endDate":{"day":26,"month":7,"year":1998},"episodes":1,"format":"OVA","genres":["Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":466,"idMal":466,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":64,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":1998,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/466","startDate":{"day":26,"month":7,"year":1998},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Defeat Him! The Pirate Ganzack!","ONE PIECE ジャンプスーパーアニメツアー'98","ONE PIECE Jump Super Anime Tour '98"],"title":{"english":"One Piece: Defeat the Pirate Ganzack!","native":"ONE PIECE 倒せ!海賊ギャンザック","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Taose! Kaizoku Ganzack","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Taose! Kaizoku Ganzack"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n1094-IAIqiFbLBsig.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a10d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx1094-H3YFJ1TR0ZZi.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx1094-H3YFJ1TR0ZZi.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx1094-H3YFJ1TR0ZZi.jpg"},"description":"The Straw Hats encounter a city in the middle of a whirlpool, called the Ocean's Navel, that is being destroyed by giant monsters. These monsters supposedly protect a treasure capable of granting wishes, but in the process of defeating these guardians, the crew ends up releasing another evil.  (aired after Episode 53)\u003cbr\u003e","duration":49,"endDate":{"day":20,"month":12,"year":2000},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":1094,"idMal":1094,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":67,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2000,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/1094","startDate":{"day":20,"month":12,"year":2000},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece: Avventura nell'ombelico dell'oceano","One Piece Special: Adventure in the Ocean's Navel","วันพีซ ภาคพิเศษ 1 การผจญภัยใต้มหาสมุทร","Vua Hải Tặc: Cuộc phiêu lưu vào rốn đại dương","One Piece Special: Luffy Falls! Adventure in the Navel of the Sea"],"title":{"english":"One Piece: Umi no Heso no Daibouken-hen","native":"ONE PIECE TVスペシャル 海のヘソの大冒険篇","romaji":"ONE PIECE TV Special: Umi no Heso no Daibouken-hen","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE TV Special: Umi no Heso no Daibouken-hen"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n1237-hHWuRsuVsVpr.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae35","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/1237.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/1237.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/1237.jpg"},"description":"The story opens on Pirate Zap's ship, where two of his crew, Bonnie and Max, are tired and want to escape, but unfortunately they have no money. Three children were being held captive on the ship overhear them. The eldest, Amanda, who's father was a pro treasure hunter, knows the whereabouts of a great treasure, and offers them a deal. If they help them make a clean escape, they could take all the treasure they wanted. They agree, and the five of them barely escape and make it onto a small island where they meet Luffy and his crew. Unfortunately they were pursued and Luffy and Amanda are captured and brought back to their boss, the head of the Bayan Pirates, who is also after the treasure. Now Luffy and the others must battle the Bayan pirates and find the treasure that Amanda's father had left for his children. Amanda, who has always resented adventure and treasure because her father was constantly gone in search for it, finally understands his feelings. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":46,"endDate":{"day":6,"month":4,"year":2003},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":1237,"idMal":1237,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":67,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2003,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/1237","startDate":{"day":6,"month":4,"year":2003},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece: Un tesoro grande un sogno","วันพีซ ภาคพิเศษ 2 ออกสู่ทะเลกว้างใหญ่ ความฝันอันยิ่งใหญ่ของพ่อ","Vua Hải Tặc: Vươn ra đại dương! Giấc mơ to lớn của bố!"],"title":{"english":"One Piece Special: Open Upon the Great Sea! A Father's Huge, HUGE Dream!","native":"ONE PIECE: 大海原にひらけ! でっかいでっカイ父の夢","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Oounabara ni Hirake! Dekkai Dekkai Chichi no Yume!","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Oounabara ni Hirake! Dekkai Dekkai Chichi no Yume!"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n1238-HdBlNr5vwNau.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5dc9f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx1238-Rf2wqBrCwgvO.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx1238-Rf2wqBrCwgvO.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx1238-Rf2wqBrCwgvO.jpg"},"description":"For many years, Ex-Marine Lieutenant Randolph and his troupe have put on a play aboard his ship. Having lost his family to pirates, Randolph wishes to put on plays that will give courage to those who have also lost their loved ones to pirates. Unfortunately, Randolph must retire soon, and he is now giving his last performance. Luffy and his crew come to see the play, and somehow manage to take part in it themselves. But from Randolph's past comes a vengeful subordinate with a diabolical plan who has finally become commander in order to capture Randolph. Luffy and his nakama now must prove to the people that not all pirates are scum, and protect Randolph's final farewell performance from the bitter commander. (aired after Episode 174)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":45,"endDate":{"day":14,"month":12,"year":2003},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":1238,"idMal":1238,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":69,"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2003,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/1238","startDate":{"day":14,"month":12,"year":2003},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece TV Special 3","One Piece: L'ultima esibizione","守れ!最後の大舞台","One Piece: Mamore! Saigo no Daibutai","One Piece Special: Protect! The Last Great Stage","วันพีซ ภาคพิเศษ 3 ป้องกันการแสดงครั้งสุดท้ายอันยิ่งใหญ่ ","Vua Hải Tặc: Bảo vệ! Vở diễn lớn cuối cùng","ONE PIECE TVスペシャル3 守れ! 最後の大舞台"],"title":{"english":"One Piece Special: Protect! The Last Great Performance","native":"ONE PIECE 守れ! 最後の大舞台","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Mamore! Saigo no Oobutai","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Mamore! Saigo no Oobutai"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n2020-k3lHutyP9i06.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bb35","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/2020.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/2020.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/2020.jpg"},"description":"Unlike the other specials, this story takes place in an alternate reality version of 19th century Japan, in \"The Grand Jipangu\", an alternate version of The Grand Line as opposed to simply being hour-long filler episodes.The story is divided into two halves: in the first, Buggy the Clown makes trouble in the town where Detective Luffy is stationed, and in the second a mysterious girl named Vivi appears. These stories feature cameos from several minor characters in the normal series. Surprisingly the \"Oyabun\" (Boss) specials did not stop there as five more specials were made following the first one, mostly as Christmas and New Years specials as well as fillers once in awhile.\u003cbr\u003e","duration":44,"endDate":{"day":18,"month":12,"year":2005},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":2020,"idMal":2020,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":68,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2005,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/2020","startDate":{"day":18,"month":12,"year":2005},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece: Le avventure del detective Cappello di Paglia"],"title":{"english":"One Piece Special: The Detective Memoirs of Chief Straw Hat Luffy","native":"ONE PIECE 年末特別企画！麦わらのルフィ親分捕物帖","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Nenmatsu Tokubetsu Kikaku! Mugiwara no Luffy Oyabun Torimonochou","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Nenmatsu Tokubetsu Kikaku! Mugiwara no Luffy Oyabun Torimonochou"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/2386-jtduFM8raO2z.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d6931a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/2386-NQQkq1taHJ08.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/2386-NQQkq1taHJ08.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/2386-NQQkq1taHJ08.jpg"},"description":"Luffy and his crew take on the Villain All-Stars in a game of soccer in order to become the Dream Soccer King. The game comes down to a pk tie-breaker shoot-out with Coby as goalie and Helmeppo refereeing.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network) ","duration":5,"endDate":{"day":2,"month":3,"year":2002},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Comedy","Fantasy","Sports"],"id":2386,"idMal":2386,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":66,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2002,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/2386","startDate":{"day":2,"month":3,"year":2002},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece: Dream Soccer King!"],"title":{"native":"ONE PIECE 夢のサッカー王!","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Yume no Soccer Ou!","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Yume no Soccer Ou!"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/2490-wlPYONPyTibY.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#ffbb43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/2490-AL4WmnCJ5zvE.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/2490-AL4WmnCJ5zvE.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/2490-AL4WmnCJ5zvE.jpg"},"description":"Luffy and crew takes on Arlong's crew in baseball. Announced by Bon Clay and Buggy.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":5,"endDate":{"day":6,"month":3,"year":2004},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Comedy","Fantasy","Sports"],"id":2490,"idMal":2490,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":64,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2004,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/2490","startDate":{"day":6,"month":3,"year":2004},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece: Take Aim! The Pirate Baseball King"],"title":{"native":"ONE PIECE めざせ! 海賊野球王","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Mezase! Kaizoku Yakyuu Ou","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Mezase! Kaizoku Yakyuu Ou"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n12001-IljdXqN8CTU7.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1e435","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/nx12001-XX0NNNfaKZ3e.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx12001-XX0NNNfaKZ3e.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/nx12001-XX0NNNfaKZ3e.jpg"},"description":"Toei Animation released a new 3D anime short at events starting December 1, 2011. The short run about 12 minutes long and played at stereoscopic 3D theaters at Aichi Prefecture's Lagunasia theme park, Nagasaki Prefecture's Huis Ten Bosch theme park, Kanagawa Prefecture's Yokohama Landmark Tower, and Hiroshima Prefecture's NTT CRED Hall.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":12,"endDate":{"day":1,"month":12,"year":2011},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy"],"id":12001,"idMal":12001,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":61,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2011,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/12001","startDate":{"day":1,"month":12,"year":2011},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"native":"ONE PIECE 3D 激走! トラップコースター","romaji":"ONE PIECE 3D: Gekisou! Trap Coaster","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE 3D: Gekisou! Trap Coaster"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/16239-pov53U1T1dRm.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c900","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b16239-XzoVjd7JK8xJ.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b16239-XzoVjd7JK8xJ.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b16239-XzoVjd7JK8xJ.png"},"description":"The story of the Hand Island no Bouken special is set a little before the events of One Piece Film Z and depicts a major \"Hand Island\" incident during the New World storyline. The story is set at \"Cannon Town\" where a parent and a child work as craftspeople. The incident revolves around them and a commodore of a marine base. The special will also have a flashback scene to the story in the first chapter of the manga, but with new animation. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network) ","duration":102,"endDate":{"day":15,"month":12,"year":2012},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":16239,"idMal":16239,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":72,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2012,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/16239","startDate":{"day":15,"month":12,"year":2012},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"One Piece: Episode of Luffy - Hand Island Adventure","native":"ONE PIECE エピソードオブルフィ 〜ハンドアイランドの冒険〜","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Episode of Luffy - Hand Island no Bouken","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Episode of Luffy - Hand Island no Bouken"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n16468-yOxhsBHFICtu.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#feae28","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b16468-pMKFwfY8lYZX.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b16468-pMKFwfY8lYZX.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b16468-pMKFwfY8lYZX.png"},"description":"An exclusive anime prologue to One Piece Film Z with an original story penned by manga creator Eiichiro Oda. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network) ","duration":5,"endDate":{"day":30,"month":12,"year":2012},"episodes":2,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":16468,"idMal":16468,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":69,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2012,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/16468","startDate":{"day":23,"month":12,"year":2012},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece: Glorious Island","One Piece Special: Glorious Island","ワンピース フィルム ゼット グロリアス アイランド"],"title":{"native":"ONE PIECE FILM Z『GLORIOUS ISLAND』","romaji":"ONE PIECE FILM: Z - GLORIOUS ISLAND","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE FILM: Z - GLORIOUS ISLAND"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/15323-zrax5OGlGepE.png","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#fed628","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/15323.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/15323.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/15323.jpg"},"description":"A retelling of the Arlong Park arc, with new animation.","duration":105,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":8,"year":2012},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":15323,"idMal":15323,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2012,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/15323","startDate":{"day":25,"month":8,"year":2012},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece Special"],"title":{"native":"ONE PIECE エピソードオブナミ 〜航海士の涙と仲間の絆〜","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Episode of Nami - Koukaishi no Namida to Nakama no Kizuna","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Episode of Nami - Koukaishi no Namida to Nakama no Kizuna"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SUMMARY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/19123-QyRShJCfnIWD.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4c95d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/nx19123-leET1CrSJknT.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx19123-leET1CrSJknT.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/nx19123-leET1CrSJknT.jpg"},"description":"The story arcs aboard the Straw Hat Crew's first ship Going Merry (Merry Go in some adaptations) are recreated with brand-new animation, from Luffy and Usopp's fight and Robin's disappearance to the crew's final farewell to the ship. Going Merry is treated as another member of the Straw Hats as Luffy, Zoro, Nami, and the rest of the crew set sail for the legendary treasure, the One Piece.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":106,"endDate":{"day":24,"month":8,"year":2013},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":19123,"idMal":19123,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2013,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/19123","startDate":{"day":24,"month":8,"year":2013},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece Special"],"title":{"english":"One Piece: Episode of Merry - The Tale of One More Friend","native":"ONE PIECE エピソードオブメリー 〜もうひとりの仲間の物語〜","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Episode of Merry - Mou Hitori no Nakama no Monogatari","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Episode of Merry - Mou Hitori no Nakama no Monogatari"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SUMMARY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/20835-aR8CuXvtzqND.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e47850","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx20835-QVV6LpJlqe1A.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx20835-QVV6LpJlqe1A.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx20835-QVV6LpJlqe1A.jpg"},"description":"This new TV special tells the two years of Luffy's training with Silvers Rayleigh in Rusukaina Island after the Battle of Marineford, which has never been told in the manga or TV anime. It also features a new villain named Burndy World who is known as \"The Destroyer of the World\" and has the power of the MoaMoa Fruit (its ability is still unknown). Luffy has to protect Boa Hancock from the new enemy who escaped from the level 6 of Impel Down. He is newly designed by the original creator of the manga, Eiichiro Oda.\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":107,"endDate":{"day":30,"month":8,"year":2014},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Action","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":20835,"idMal":25161,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2014,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/20835","startDate":{"day":30,"month":8,"year":2014},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece Special 15th Anniversary"],"title":{"english":"One Piece 3D2Y: Overcome Ace’s Death! Luffy’s Vow to his Friends","native":"ONE PIECE “3D2Y” エースの死を越えて! ルフィ仲間との誓い","romaji":"ONE PIECE \"3D2Y\": Ace no shi wo Koete! Luffy Nakama to no Chikai","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE \"3D2Y\": Ace no shi wo Koete! Luffy Nakama to no Chikai"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21230-5yju21iK6aMW.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a150","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx21230-rfoUZud1Jn0L.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx21230-rfoUZud1Jn0L.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx21230-rfoUZud1Jn0L.png"},"description":"The anime will explore the childhood bond between Luffy, Ace and Sabo.","duration":110,"endDate":{"day":22,"month":8,"year":2015},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Drama"],"id":21230,"idMal":31289,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":74,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2015,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21230","startDate":{"day":22,"month":8,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece: Episode of Sabo - The Three Brothers' Bond: The Miraculous Reunion and the Inherited Will"],"title":{"english":"One Piece - Episode of Sabo: Bond of Three Brothers - A Miraculous Reunion and an Inherited Will","native":"ONE PIECE エピソードオブサボ ~3兄弟の絆 奇跡の再会と受け継がれる意志~","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Episode of Sabo - 3-Kyoudai no Kizuna Kiseki no Saikai to Uketsugareru Ishi","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Episode of Sabo - 3-Kyoudai no Kizuna Kiseki no Saikai to Uketsugareru Ishi"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SUMMARY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21485-lPFbmxGrFsBX.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/21485-KR1sv4rYSe6V.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/21485-KR1sv4rYSe6V.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/21485-KR1sv4rYSe6V.jpg"},"description":"The Davy Back Fight Arc competitors journey to New World with new crew members Dojaku, Kansho and tactical genius Komei for a meeting that will take place on a foggy island that makes devil fruit users unable to use to their abilities.","duration":116,"endDate":{"day":19,"month":12,"year":2015},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":21485,"idMal":32051,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":69,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2015,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21485","startDate":{"day":19,"month":12,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece - Aventura en Nebulandia"],"title":{"english":"One Piece: Adventure of Nebulandia","native":"ONE PIECE 〜アドベンチャー オブ ネブランディア〜","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Adventure of Nebulandia","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Adventure of Nebulandia"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21831-Xl4r2uBaaKU4.png","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a10d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx21831-qj5IKYiPOupF.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx21831-qj5IKYiPOupF.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx21831-qj5IKYiPOupF.jpg"},"description":"The Straw Hat Pirates meet Olga, a girl who has escaped the island Alchemi. Alchemi was known for its metal production, and for the creation of the extremely valuable Pure Gold, but the island disappeared two hundred years ago. Olga is now being pursued by Marines, interested in Pure Gold. Gildo Tesoro, who controls the Navy HQ and black market, hears of Olga and hires treasure hunter Mad Treasure to track her down. The Straw Hats join forces with Olga in search of the Pure Gold, while she plots to takes advantage of them and use the treasure to become rich herself.","duration":104,"endDate":{"day":16,"month":7,"year":2016},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":21831,"idMal":33338,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":73,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2016,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21831","startDate":{"day":16,"month":7,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"One Piece: Heart of Gold","native":"ONE PIECE 〜ハートオブゴールド〜","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Heart of Gold","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Heart of Gold"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/99302-v3NwmsSnjj94.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#bbe45d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx99302-b40WIhc5dylo.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx99302-b40WIhc5dylo.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx99302-b40WIhc5dylo.jpg"},"description":"The special will be a completely new work, featuring reanimated scenes from the beginning of the series through when the crew enters the Grand Line.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nThe special is commemorating the manga's 20th anniversary, and will also feature anime versions of the original manga's chapter cover stories as part of the special's ending credits. The staff haven't yet clarified which cover story or stories will be animated. Additionally, the anime will feature a special 20th anniversary commemoration version of the original opening theme song \"We Are!\".\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":106,"endDate":{"day":26,"month":8,"year":2017},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Action","Adventure","Drama"],"id":99302,"idMal":36215,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2017,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/99302","startDate":{"day":26,"month":8,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"One Piece: Episode of East Blue","native":"ONE PIECE エピソードオブ東の海〜ルフィと4人の仲間の大冒険!!〜","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Episode of East Blue - Luffy to 4-nin no Nakama no Daibouken","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Episode of East Blue - Luffy to 4-nin no Nakama no Daibouken"},"trailer":{"id":"XcWmgU7X-Is","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/XcWmgU7X-Is/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SUMMARY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/459-JqlCjcwxxFrr.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e40d0d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx459-Ivw65mUXackh.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx459-Ivw65mUXackh.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx459-Ivw65mUXackh.png"},"description":"There once was a pirate known as the Great Gold Pirate Woonan, who obtained almost 1/3 of the world's gold. Over the course of a few years, the pirate's existence faded, and a legend grew that he disappeared with his gold to a remote island, an island pirates continue to search for. Aboard the Going Merry, Luffy and his crew, starved and reckless, are robbed of their treasure. In an attempt to get it back, they wreck the getaway ship, guided by a young boy named Tabio, who's a captured part of El Drago's pirate crew. El Drago's love for gold has driven him to look for Woonan's island, and thanks to Woonan's treasure map, he finds it. During this time, Luffy's crew have been split up, and despite their own circumstances, they must find a way to stop El Drago from obtaining Woonan's gold. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":50,"endDate":{"day":4,"month":3,"year":2000},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":459,"idMal":459,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":68,"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2000,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/459","startDate":{"day":4,"month":3,"year":2000},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece: The Movie","One Piece (2000)","One Piece: La Película","วันพีซ เดอะมูฟวี่ 1 เกาะสมบัติแห่งวูนัน","Vua Hải Tặc: Đảo Châu Báu","One Piece: Golden Island Adventure","One Piece - Per tutto l'oro del mondo"],"title":{"english":"ONE PIECE: The Movie","native":"ONE PIECE (Movie)","romaji":"ONE PIECE (Movie)","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE (Movie)"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/460-mWAlHAJ5MuBg.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4c943","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx460-p9HObfGUhWn0.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx460-p9HObfGUhWn0.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx460-p9HObfGUhWn0.jpg"},"description":"Informed by the Thief Brothers his ship has been stolen by the Trump Kyoudai (Trump Siblings) who have set up base on Clockwork Island. Monkey D. Luffy, Captain of the Going Merry and aspiring Pirate King works with his crew - Ussop, Zoro, Sanji and Nami to battle their way up Clockwork Island to reclaim their ship.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":55,"endDate":{"day":3,"month":3,"year":2001},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":460,"idMal":460,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":67,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2001,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/460","startDate":{"day":3,"month":3,"year":2001},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece Movie 02","วันพีซ เดอะมูฟวี่ 2 การผจญภัยบนเกาะแห่งฟันเฟือง","Vua Hải Tặc: Cuộc phiêu lưu đến đảo máy đồng hồ ","One Piece - Avventura all'Isola Spirale"],"title":{"english":"One Piece: Clockwork Island Adventure","native":"ONE PIECE ねじまき島の冒険","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Nejimaki-jima no Bouken","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Nejimaki-jima no Bouken"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/461-0pvcIaXC0p70.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e49343","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx461-DC9fMDl3AaK1.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx461-DC9fMDl3AaK1.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx461-DC9fMDl3AaK1.jpg"},"description":"The crew comes upon Crown Island where the animals can talk and they makes Chopper their new king. But there are human hunters there also looking for the legendary horns that will give the person who consumes it immense power. Luffy and friends must stop them from destroying this animal kingdom.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":55,"endDate":{"day":2,"month":3,"year":2002},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":461,"idMal":461,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":64,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2002,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/461","startDate":{"day":2,"month":3,"year":2002},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece Movie 03","วันพีซ เดอะมูฟวี่ 3 เกาะแห่งสรรพสัตว์และราชันย์ช็อปเปอร์ ","Vua Hải Tặc: Vương quốc Chopper trên đảo của những sinh vật lạ","One Piece: Chopper Kingdom of Strange Animal Island","One Piece - Il tesoro del re"],"title":{"english":"One Piece: Chopper’s Kingdom on the Island of Strange Animals","native":"ONE PIECE 珍獣島のチョッパー王国","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Chinjuu-jima no Chopper Oukoku","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Chinjuu-jima no Chopper Oukoku"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/462-Z074owEvilUu.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e49343","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx462-Ig8zfdsFWcql.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx462-Ig8zfdsFWcql.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx462-Ig8zfdsFWcql.png"},"description":"Luffy and crew arrive at the harbour of Anabaru. The local casino is holding a competition in which the winner will obtain a huge monetary reward if he reaches the finishing line first. Nami is elated and decides to participate in the competition. However, there is a conspiracy going behind the competition and the mastermind is an ex-military commander, Gasparde. His plan is to lure all the pirates to the military base and send them to their deaths. Luffy and gang have to overcome the numerous tests and tribulations along the way to complete this dead-end adventure. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":95,"endDate":{"day":1,"month":3,"year":2003},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":462,"idMal":462,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":72,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2003,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/462","startDate":{"day":1,"month":3,"year":2003},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece Movie 04","One Piece: La Aventura sin Salida","The Adventure of Deadend","One Piece: Dead End","วันพีซ เดอะมูฟวี่ 4 การผจญภัยที่เดดเอนด์","Vua Hải Tặc: Cuộc đua tử thần","One Piece - Trappola mortale"],"title":{"english":"One Piece The Movie: The Dead End Adventure","native":"ONE PIECE THE MOVIE デッドエンドの冒険","romaji":"ONE PIECE THE MOVIE: Dead End no Bouken","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE THE MOVIE: Dead End no Bouken"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/463-zgU5XjUCR7Kv.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45078","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/nx463-QDnETPoHp9oD.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx463-QDnETPoHp9oD.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/nx463-QDnETPoHp9oD.jpg"},"description":"Luffy and crew go to an island searching for a legendary sword, said to be the most expensive in the world. Soon attacking marines and beautiful maidens split the crew. Zoro betrays the crew to help an old friend, Luffy and Usopp wander through a cave, and the rest help a village fight marines. When Zoro defeats Sanji he takes the sacred pearls that are the only defense against the evil sword that will plunge the world into darkness. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":95,"endDate":{"day":6,"month":3,"year":2004},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":463,"idMal":463,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":67,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2004,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/463","startDate":{"day":6,"month":3,"year":2004},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece Movie 05","One Piece: La Maldición de la Espada Sagrada","One Piece: The Cursed Holy Sword","One Piece : La malédiction de l'épée sacrée","วันพีซ เดอะมูฟวี่ 5 วันดวลดาบ ต้องสาปมรณะ ","Vua Hải Tặc: Thánh kiếm bị nguyền rủa","One Piece - Der Fluch des heiligen Schwerts","One Piece - La spada delle sette stelle"],"title":{"english":"One Piece: The Curse of the Sacred Sword","native":"ONE PIECE 呪われた聖剣","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Norowareta Seiken","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Norowareta Seiken"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/464-wmQoE1Ywxghs.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a15d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx464-g4wcZPjbhY5j.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx464-g4wcZPjbhY5j.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx464-g4wcZPjbhY5j.png"},"description":"The Straw Hat crew obtain an advertisement for a recreational island on the Grand Line run by the Baron Omatsuri. Luffy decides to take this opportunity to kick back and relax. Unfortunately, when they arrive at the island, they are asked to compete in contests through unity for access to relaxation. However, there seems to be a mysterious air on the island, as the Straw Hat Pirates begin to fight amongst themselves, while Robin, Chopper, and Luffy individually search for the secret behind Baron Omatsuri's island.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":91,"endDate":{"day":5,"month":3,"year":2005},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":464,"idMal":464,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2005,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/464","startDate":{"day":5,"month":3,"year":2005},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece Movie 6","One Piece: El barón Omatsuri y la isla de los secretos","One Piece - L'isola segreta del barone Omatsuri"],"title":{"english":"One Piece: Baron Omatsuri and the Secret Island","native":"ONE PIECE THE MOVIE オマツリ男爵と秘密の島","romaji":"ONE PIECE THE MOVIE: Omatsuri Danshaku to Himitsu no Shima","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE THE MOVIE: Omatsuri Danshaku to Himitsu no Shima"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/465-dYMZ6SHNeOkL.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#43aeff","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx465-qSRr0MKYhS0I.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx465-qSRr0MKYhS0I.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx465-qSRr0MKYhS0I.jpg"},"description":"The crew salvages a treasure chest from a sinking wreck, but inside turns out to be an old lady hiding. To get the Straw Hat Pirates to take her home, she promises them the treasure of a golden crown on her island, Mecha Island. When they arrive, their ship is first attacked by the lord of the island. But later he decides to use the pirates to help him solve the riddle of the Golden Crown.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":94,"endDate":{"day":4,"month":3,"year":2006},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":465,"idMal":465,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":68,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2006,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/465","startDate":{"day":4,"month":3,"year":2006},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece: Karakuri Shiro no Mecha Kyohei","One Piece Movie 07","One Piece: El gran soldado mecánico del castillo Karakuri","The Giant Mechanical Soldier of Karakuri Castle","One Piece: Schloss Karakuris Metall-Soldaten","One Piece - I misteri dell'isola meccanica"],"title":{"english":"One Piece: Mega Mecha Soldier of Karakuri Castle","native":"ONE PIECE THE MOVIE カラクリ城のメカ巨兵","romaji":"ONE PIECE THE MOVIE: Karakuri-jou no Mecha Kyohei","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE THE MOVIE: Karakuri-jou no Mecha Kyohei"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/2107-Je0JIEoxx1VF.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a143","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx2107-H8bRuRRbhCIJ.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx2107-H8bRuRRbhCIJ.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx2107-H8bRuRRbhCIJ.jpg"},"description":"A retelling of the Alabasta arc. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nRevolution is brewing in the desert country of Alabasta, but the Straw Hats and Princess Vivi know the truth: it's all a plot cooked up by Crocodile. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Netflix)","duration":90,"endDate":{"day":3,"month":3,"year":2007},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":2107,"idMal":2107,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":70,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2007,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/2107","startDate":{"day":3,"month":3,"year":2007},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece Movie 8: Episode of Alabasta - The Desert Princess and the Pirates","One Piece Película 8: La saga del Arabasta - Los piratas y la princesa del desierto","One Piece Movie 08","One Piece - Un'amicizia oltre i confini del mare"],"title":{"english":"One Piece: The Desert Princess and the Pirates, Adventures in Alabasta","native":"ONE PIECE エピソードオブアラバスタ 砂漠の王女と海賊たち","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Episode of Alabasta - Sabaku no Oujo to Kaizoku-tachi","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Episode of Alabasta - Sabaku no Oujo to Kaizoku-tachi"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SUMMARY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/3848-LXsSQtSFu4e9.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4e450","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx3848-SCnYGTn34Llt.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx3848-SCnYGTn34Llt.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx3848-SCnYGTn34Llt.jpg"},"description":"The movie is a retelling of the Drum Island arc with new music and animation. Vivi has been removed from the plot while both Nico Robin and Franky, who joined the crew after the Drum Island arc, have been added. The movie also has the Straw Hat's new ship, the Thousand Sunny. It has been stated that Oda will be creating a new character for this movie, Wapol's older brother, Mushul, who also appears to be a Devil Fruit user. \u003cbr\u003e","duration":113,"endDate":{"day":1,"month":3,"year":2008},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":3848,"idMal":3848,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":71,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2008,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/3848","startDate":{"day":1,"month":3,"year":2008},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Miracle Sakura","One Piece: Episodio de Chopper + El milagro del cerezo en invierno","One Piece: Episode of Chopper Plus - Bloom in the Winter, Miracle Sakura","One Piece Movie 09","One Piece - Il miracolo dei ciliegi in fiore"],"title":{"english":"One Piece: Episode Of Chopper +: The Miracle Winter Cherry Blossom","native":"ONE PIECE THE MOVIE エピソードオブチョッパー+ 冬に咲く、奇跡の桜","romaji":"ONE PIECE THE MOVIE: Episode of Chopper Plus - Fuyu ni Saku, Kiseki no Sakura","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE THE MOVIE: Episode of Chopper Plus - Fuyu ni Saku, Kiseki no Sakura"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SUMMARY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/4155-2PkLjTHddz2s.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx4155-P5TDf6t6qFwX.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx4155-P5TDf6t6qFwX.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx4155-P5TDf6t6qFwX.png"},"description":"The story begins somewhere between the Thriller Bark arc and the Sabaody Archipelago arc. The main villain's name is \"Golden Lion\" Shiki. 20 years ago he lost a battle against Monkey D. Garp and Sengoku and was imprisoned in Impel Down, but managed to escape. After that he starts to collect his crew and steals Nami to make her his navigator. Luffy tries to get to Shiki's hideout to free his friend. ","duration":113,"endDate":{"day":12,"month":12,"year":2009},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":4155,"idMal":4155,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2009,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/4155","startDate":{"day":12,"month":12,"year":2009},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece Film 10","ワンピース ストロング ワールド","One Piece: Strong World","One Piece - Avventura sulle isole volanti"],"title":{"english":"One Piece Film: Strong World","native":"ONE PIECE FILM STRONG WORLD","romaji":"ONE PIECE FILM: STRONG WORLD","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE FILM: STRONG WORLD"},"trailer":{"id":"3n58UPvcD7I","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/3n58UPvcD7I/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/9999-T5jCX3o3cxeN.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#ffa100","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/9999.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/9999.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/9999.jpg"},"description":"The entire Straw Hat crew began to search for Luffy's important straw hat after he woke up finding it missing.","duration":30,"endDate":{"day":19,"month":3,"year":2011},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":9999,"idMal":9999,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":65,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2011,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/9999","startDate":{"day":19,"month":3,"year":2011},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece 3D: Straw Hat Chase","One Piece 3D - L'inseguimento di Cappello di Paglia"],"title":{"english":"One Piece 3D: Mugiwara Chase","native":"ONE PIECE 3D 麦わらチェイス","romaji":"ONE PIECE 3D: Mugiwara Chase","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE 3D: Mugiwara Chase"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/12859-XjlBW6o2YwUb.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1ae5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx12859-uQFENDPzMWz6.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx12859-uQFENDPzMWz6.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx12859-uQFENDPzMWz6.jpg"},"description":"Said to be comparable to the Ancient Weapons of old, the Marines’ trump card, the “Dyna Stones,” have suddenly been stolen by a group of renegade vigilantes. The terrifyingly powerful man responsible, former Marine Admiral “Z”, now stands in the path of Luffy and his Straw Hat Pirates. Can the Straw Hats defeat “Z” and his crew, or will the New World meet its end at the hands of this mad man? \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Funimation)","duration":107,"endDate":{"day":15,"month":12,"year":2012},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Drama"],"id":12859,"idMal":12859,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2012,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/12859","startDate":{"day":15,"month":12,"year":2012},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece Film 12: Z","海贼王剧场版Z","One Piece Gold - Il film"],"title":{"english":"One Piece Film: Z","native":"ONE PIECE FILM Z","romaji":"ONE PIECE FILM: Z","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE FILM: Z"},"trailer":{"id":"1gGt1Mg_zSo","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/1gGt1Mg_zSo/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21335-ps20iVSGUXbD.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bb35","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/nx21335-XsXdE0AeOkkZ.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx21335-XsXdE0AeOkkZ.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/nx21335-XsXdE0AeOkkZ.jpg"},"description":"In One Piece Film Gold, The Straw Hats are at it again in an all-new high-flying adventure! A gripping tale unfolds in the spectacular city of Gran Tesoro, where Luffy and his crew are drawn by dreams of hitting the jackpot. With so much luck, Luffy's winning streak can't possibly end. But behind the gilded curtains lies a powerful king whose deep pockets and deeper ambitions spell disaster for all.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: FUNimation)","duration":120,"endDate":{"day":23,"month":7,"year":2016},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":21335,"idMal":31490,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2016,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21335","startDate":{"day":23,"month":7,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["One Piece Film 13","航海王之黄金城"],"title":{"english":"One Piece Film: Gold","native":"ONE PIECE FILM GOLD","romaji":"ONE PIECE FILM: GOLD","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE FILM: GOLD"},"trailer":{"id":"_shEgcWHC2U","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/_shEgcWHC2U/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SIDE_STORY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/n96427-UsjDRx1o4V8V.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4861a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx96427-XiDc44cTlf29.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx96427-XiDc44cTlf29.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx96427-XiDc44cTlf29.png"},"description":"One Piece: Loguetown Arc is a novelization of Eiichiro Oda's intended story elements for the Loguetown Arc, later used in the anime as a filler (Episodes 50-51).\n","endDate":{},"format":"NOVEL","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":96427,"idMal":94534,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":74,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/96427","startDate":{"day":17,"month":7,"year":2000},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["ONE PIECE: Loguetown Arc","Logue Town"],"title":{"native":"ONE PIECE ローグタウン編","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Loguetown-hen","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Loguetown-hen"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/30013-hbbRZqC5MjYh.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx30013-BeslEMqiPhlk.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx30013-BeslEMqiPhlk.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx30013-BeslEMqiPhlk.jpg"},"description":"As a child, Monkey D. Luffy was inspired to become a pirate by listening to the tales of the buccaneer \"Red-Haired\" Shanks. But his life changed when Luffy accidentally ate the Gum-Gum Devil Fruit and gained the power to stretch like rubber...at the cost of never being able to swim again! Years later, still vowing to become the king of the pirates, Luffy sets out on his adventure...one guy alone in a rowboat, in search of the legendary \"One Piece,\" said to be the greatest treasure in the world...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: VIZ Media)","endDate":{},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":30013,"idMal":13,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":91,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/30013","startDate":{"day":22,"month":7,"year":1997},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["원피스","וואן פיס ","One Piece - Большой куш","ワンピース","ONE PIECE～航海王～","วันพีซ"],"title":{"english":"One Piece","native":"ONE PIECE","romaji":"ONE PIECE","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE"},"trailer":{"id":"z_qWsQNWSVI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/z_qWsQNWSVI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"MANGA"},"relationType":"SOURCE"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101918-jUG4Mb1hCxVS.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5dc9f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx101918-3uyCYHw1syki.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx101918-3uyCYHw1syki.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx101918-3uyCYHw1syki.png"},"description":"The special will be the first in the \"Episode of\" series to cover the Skypeia arc, and will feature a character who did not appear in the original Skypeia arc from the anime.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":105,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":8,"year":2018},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":101918,"idMal":37902,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":70,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2018,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/101918","startDate":{"day":25,"month":8,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"One Piece: Episode of Skypiea","native":"ONE PIECE エピソードオブ空島","romaji":"ONE PIECE: Episode of Sorajima","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE: Episode of Sorajima"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"SUMMARY"},{"node":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/8740-MlFelJndh6Yr.png","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e493a1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b8740-oZajT3brPn7b.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b8740-oZajT3brPn7b.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b8740-oZajT3brPn7b.jpg"},"description":"Set over 20 years prior to the main One Piece story, this limited release OVA chronicles the confrontation between Gold Lion Shiki and Gold Roger as well as other events around the world around the time of the Pirate King's execution. ","duration":18,"endDate":{"day":16,"month":4,"year":2010},"episodes":1,"format":"OVA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":8740,"idMal":8740,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2010,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/8740","startDate":{"day":16,"month":4,"year":2010},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"native":"ONE PIECE FILM STRONG WORLD EPISODE:0","romaji":"ONE PIECE FILM: STRONG WORLD - EPISODE:0"