MLkusd2Y.jpg"},"description":"Brook introduces the Thousand Sunny's while Luffy searches for his straw hat.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nThis was a special included in a limited edition DVD that was released in Nissan stores across Japan. The DVD also included the making of One Piece 3D: Straw Hat Chase.\n","duration":12,"endDate":{"day":5,"month":3,"year":2011},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":102639,"idMal":20871,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":56,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/102639","startDate":{"day":5,"month":3,"year":2011},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Nissan Serena x One Piece 3D: Mugiwara Chase - Sennyuu!! Sauzando Sanii-gou"],"title":{"native":"日産SERENA×ワンピース 潜入サウザンド・サニー号","romaji":"Nissan SERENA x One Piece: Sennyuu Sauzando Sanii-gou","userPreferred":"Nissan SERENA x One Piece: Sennyuu Sauzando Sanii-gou"},"type":"ANIME"},"relationType":"CHARACTER"},{"node":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4c943","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b106492-ciLSI5nTJsV7.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b106492-ciLSI5nTJsV7.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b106492-ciLSI5nTJsV7.png"},"description":"\"Orb Panic Adventure!\" is a special crossover story featuring characters from One Piece, Dragon Ball and Astro Boy. It was created as part of many interactive crossovers screened at special events called Odaiba Boken-Oh to commemorate Fuji TV's 45th anniversary. It has yet to see a home release. In the following year it had a sequel called Kyutai Panic Adventure Returns!\u003cbr\u003e\n","duration":9,"endDate":{"year":2003},"episodes":1,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Action"],"id":106492,"idMal":23933,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":44,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/106492","startDate":{"year":2003},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Orb Panic Adventure!","Сфера панического приключения"],"title":{